title: AJAX Development
details: What you'll learn - Understand the basics of Ajax interactions. To Update the Browser Window's HTML content dynamically through the DOM. To Understand the Role of a Web Server in Ajax. To Dynamically Create and Send Parameterized Queries to a Server. To Receive and Parse JSON Objects in the DOM

title: Learn Perl 5 By Doing It
details: Learn Perl by actually creating useful, working Perl programs for everything from web scraping to fixing your data.. What you'll learn - Learn how to use Perl for a variety of common tasks. Learn how to use regular expressions.
